  "short_description": "At the intersection of colliding universes, you bring your Hero to fight for the survival of your world. Become imbued with power from your Aspects and equip yourself with your Factions' legendary gear in this next-gen, action-packed, third-person MOBA. Prepare yourself for battle at the FAULT.",
